            "title": "歐盟財政部長考慮對美國動用反脅迫工具和其他經濟反制措施",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"歐盟財政部長考慮對美國動用反脅迫工具和其他經濟反制措施\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"538\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/EdvPP6mujO5pNnRuArcwdA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUzOA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-01/a8475950-f5fb-11f0-b17f-2a1d0e6d4e43\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">歐盟財政部長考慮對美國動用反脅迫工具和其他經濟反制措施</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
